  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "第一节 政府机构",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "840992_9_10368-10433",
          "range": "10368-10433",
          "rangeStart": 10368,
          "rangeEnd": 10433,
          "markText": "户部只起到解运银两的簿记职能，它不能通过预算来控制拨款。所有各项开支的节余都由各个部门自己控制，存入它们自己的银库，户部无权管理。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773056913,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-09 19:48:33",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840992&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10368&rangeEnd=10433",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b832c505cd5204b8c10492?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10368&rangeEnd=10433"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "840992_9_16280-16366",
          "range": "16280-16366",
          "rangeStart": 16280,
          "rangeEnd": 16366,
          "markText": "在明代，所有这些义务后来逐渐被折纳成银两，由工部接收。这些收入数目很大，它们直接源于税收收入，可以让工部自给自足。这实际上意味着工部逐渐变成了一个税收机构，与户部展开竞争。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773056910,
